data.description: OPEN HOUSE on SATURDAY 11/18/2023 1:00pm- 3:00pm  MOTIVATED SELLER.! Welcome to this charming and meticulously maintained two-story home in the heart of Duncannon/New Buffalo Borough. This delightful property boasts 4 bedrooms, 1.5 baths, and a plethora of features to make it your dream home. As you approach, you'll be immediately captivated by the impeccable curb appeal. The exterior exudes a sense of warmth and welcomes you to explore all that this property has to offer. Upon entering the home, you're greeted by a spacious living room, perfect for relaxing and spending quality time with family and friends. To the right, you'll find a versatile bonus room, which could serve as an ideal office space or a potential 5th bedroom, providing flexibility to suit your lifestyle. Continue your journey through this home, you discover a generously sized eat-in kitchen, designed to be the perfect space for preparing meals and creating lasting memories with loved ones. Adjacent to the kitchen is the conveniently located laundry room and a half bath, making daily chores a breeze. The Refrigerator, Washer & Dryer are included. The upper level of the home offers four well-proportioned bedrooms, each with ample closet space to keep your living space organized and clutter-free. A full bath completes this level. This home comes equipped with a washer, dryer, dishwasher, refrigerator, and microwave, simplifying your move-in process Stepping outside, you'll be delighted to find a fantastic backyard that truly sets this property apart. A cement patio, added in 2021, and a deck provide wonderful spaces for outdoor entertaining, allowing you to host gatherings and create lasting memories. The level, fenced-in backyard is an perfect for gardening enthusiasts, with established blackberry bushes and plenty of room to cultivate your own vegetables. It also features a fire pit area and a convenient shed for all your storage needs. That's not all - the backyard also boasts mature apple and cherry trees, ensuring you have a delicious supply of fruit right at your doorstep.  Practical upgrades have been made to this property, including a new roof in 2020, a cement porch addition in 2021, and newer plumbing, all contributing to your peace of mind and future home maintenance. For your comfort, window air conditioning units are included, as well as, the Refrigerator, Washer, and Dryer and remain with the property. This lovely home is priced to sell and offers a wonderful opportunity to make it your own. Don't miss out on the chance to call this well cared-for property your new home sweet home.
